00:03:57.070 --> 00:03:59.650
Now, you probably think
of the Google Assistant

00:03:59.650 --> 00:04:02.320
as primarily coming through
these-- the Google Homes

00:04:02.320 --> 00:04:04.570
and tons made by third parties.

00:04:04.570 --> 00:04:07.460
And that's definitely
the way to think of us.

00:04:07.460 --> 00:04:09.970
But we want you to think
of it as more than just

00:04:09.970 --> 00:04:11.030
