learning how to go build these

00:04:43.660 --> 00:04:45.370
games--

00:04:45.370 --> 00:04:48.010
we do know a couple things.

00:04:48.010 --> 00:04:50.290
When we look at
who our users are,

00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:53.230
we're seeing a couple of
patterns of who they are.

00:04:53.230 --> 00:04:57.550
They're millennials, they're
families, and they're kids--

00:04:57.550 --> 00:04:58.570
perfect game players.

00:05:01.490 --> 00:05:03.970
