00:05:08.320 --> 00:05:11.410
And what's important to
note is it took a while

00:05:11.410 --> 00:05:15.310
before "Angry Birds" became
one of the seminal games

00:05:15.310 --> 00:05:17.170
on touchscreens.

00:05:17.170 --> 00:05:18.750
Smartphones were released.

00:05:18.750 --> 00:05:21.040
And it took about two
years before "Angry Birds"

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:25.082
even came out and rise.

00:05:25.082 --> 00:05:26.540
And this is where
we are right now.

00:05:26.540 --> 00:05:29.955
Smart speakers have
been out for a while,

00:05:29.955 --> 00:05:31.580
but there's an
inflection point that we

00:05:31.580 --> 00:05:35.040
believe is going to happen,
particularly around play.

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:36.730
And we're down there.

00:05:36.730 --> 00:05:39.870
And we believe that one
of you, many of you,

00:05:39.870 --> 00:05:44.130
hopefully all of you will
be on that curve coming up.

00:05:44.130 --> 00:05:48.180
So I'm going to hand this
