00:34:38.136 --> 00:34:40.010
The other big thing we
want to leave you with

00:34:40.010 --> 00:34:43.580
is if you make something
and no one hears it,

00:34:43.580 --> 00:34:45.090
not only is that a
punch in the gut,

00:34:45.090 --> 00:34:50.100
but you're wondering what you
