to all developers.

00:35:00.230 --> 00:35:02.120
This is called a
built-in intent.

00:35:02.120 --> 00:35:05.750
There are other talks about it,
but register your app for it.

00:35:05.750 --> 00:35:11.000
Consider it the app store of
games on the Google Assistant.

00:35:11.000 --> 00:35:13.130
And when someone says
"play a game," which

00:35:13.130 --> 00:35:15.920
is what a lot of
our users are doing,

00:35:15.920 --> 00:35:19.040
they'll get a list of
the games available.

00:35:19.040 --> 00:35:21.860
And this works on both
smart displays, phones,

00:35:21.860 --> 00:35:22.775
and smart speakers.

00:35:25.740 --> 00:35:29.430
But to make that happen, we
have a little homework for you.

00:35:29.430 --> 00:35:31.800
Go back into your actions
on Google console,

00:35:31.800 --> 00:35:33.510
and fill out all the metadata.

00:35:33.510 --> 00:35:37.740
That's what we use
to look at your app,

00:35:37.740 --> 00:35:40.910
know what it is about,
and feature it with users.

00:35:40.910 --> 00:35:42.570
So make sure you
have beautiful icons

00:35:42.570 --> 00:35:44.360
and your descriptions
are great there.

00:35:46.970 --> 00:35:49.370
And I'm going to tell
you a little secret--

00:35:49.370 --> 00:35:51.980
we don't usually talk
about how we rank things,

00:35:51.980 --> 00:35:53.810
but I wanted to highlight this.

00:35:53.810 --> 00:35:57.890
This is how we look for quality.

00:35:57.890 --> 00:36:01.250
Straight up quality,
be it it sounds great,

00:36:01.250 --> 00:36:05.480
the gameplay is great, and users
are loving it and rating it.

00:36:05.480 --> 00:36:09.200
We're looking for long sessions
and games that have people

00:36:09.200 --> 00:36:11.422
coming back for more and more.

00:36:11.422 --> 00:36:13.880
We're looking for games that
map to those core demographics

00:36:13.880 --> 00:36:16.546
of millennials,
families, and kids.

00:36:16.546 --> 00:36:18.170
And we're looking
for games that aren't

00:36:18.170 --> 00:36:19.700
like the others around there.

00:36:19.700 --> 00:36:23.720
We want to offer our users
a wide variety of games.

00:36:23.720 --> 00:36:27.350
And then, if you can update
your apps regularly and feature

00:36:27.350 --> 00:36:30.050
the new tech, like jumping
onto those smart displays,

00:36:30.050 --> 00:36:33.320
that will give you a great shot
of getting in front of users.

